                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-700 font-bold">Options for 0% Down Payment (T&C apply)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#8B6F47] mt-8 mb-4">3 Tips for a Smooth Approval</h2>
        
        <p>Want to get your equipment in your warehouse faster? Here is some practical advice:</p>
        
