          <li><strong>Be Clear on the Equipment:</strong> Show us the quotation or the details of the machine. Whether it's a second-hand Toyota forklift or a brand-new German reach truck, we need to know what we're financing.</li>
          <li><strong>Think About the Tenure:</strong> Do you want lower monthly payments over 5 years, or do you want to finish paying in 3 years and save on interest? We can help you calculate which one fits your monthly cash flow better.</li>
        </ol>

